---
import { Icon } from 'astro-icon/components';
import Button from '../ui/Button.astro';
import SectionLayout from '../ui/SectionLayout.astro';
---

<section class="relative w-full min-h-screen flex items-center justify-center overflow-hidden bg-gradient-to-br from-neutral-50 via-white to-primary-green/5">
  <!-- Decorative Background Elements -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-5">
    <div class="absolute top-20 left-20 w-64 h-64 bg-primary-green rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl animate-pulse"></div>
    <div class="absolute bottom-32 right-20 w-80 h-80 bg-primary-green-dark rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 1s"></div>
    <div class="absolute top-1/2 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 -translate-y-1/2 w-96 h-96 bg-blue-400 rounded-full mix-blend-multiply filter blur-3xl animate-pulse" style="animation-delay: 2s"></div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Pattern Overlay -->
  <div class="absolute inset-0 opacity-10">
    <svg class="w-full h-full" viewBox="0 0 100 100">
      <defs>
        <pattern id="grid" width="10" height="10" patternUnits="userSpaceOnUse">
          <path d="M 10 0 L 0 0 0 10" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="0.5"/>
        </pattern>
      </defs>
      <rect width="100%" height="100%" fill="url(#grid)" class="text-primary-green"/>
    </svg>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Main Content -->
  <div class="relative z-10 w-full max-w-6xl mx-auto px-6 lg:px-8 text-center">
    <div class="max-w-4xl mx-auto space-y-8" data-aos="fade-up" data-aos-duration="1200">
      
      <!-- Tagline Badge -->
      <div 
        class="inline-flex items-center gap-2 bg-primary-green/10 border border-primary-green/20 rounded-full px-6 py-3 mb-6"
        data-aos="fade-down"
        data-aos-delay="100"
      >
        <Icon name="ph:buildings-fill" class="w-5 h-5 text-primary-green" />
        <span class="font-heebo font-medium text-primary-green text-[16px]">Quiénes Somos</span>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Main Heading -->
      <h1 
        class="font-urbanist font-bold text-neutral-darkest leading-tight mb-6"
        style="font-size: clamp(48px, 8vw, 72px); line-height: 1.1;"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="200"
      >
        Construyendo el futuro de 
        <span class="text-primary-green">Costa Rica</span>
      </h1>
      
      <!-- Subtitle -->
      <p 
        class="font-heebo font-normal text-neutral-darkest/80 max-w-3xl mx-auto leading-relaxed text-[18px] lg:text-[20px] mb-8"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="300"
      >
        Somos una empresa familiar con más de 15 años de experiencia, dedicada a crear espacios 
        que inspiran y transforman comunidades. Cada proyecto es una oportunidad para construir 
        sueños y generar un impacto positivo duradero.
      </p>
      
      <!-- Stats Row -->
      <div 
        class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-3 gap-8 max-w-3xl mx-auto mb-10"
        data-aos="fade-up"
        data-aos-delay="400"
      >
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-green/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <Icon name="ph:calendar-check-fill" class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-green" />
          </div>
          <div class="font-urbanist font-bold text-[32px] text-primary-green mb-2">15+</div>
          <div class="font-heebo text-[16px] text-neutral-darkest/70">Años de experiencia</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-green/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <Icon name="ph:buildings-fill" class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-green" />
          </div>
          <div class="font-urbanist font-bold text-[32px] text-primary-green mb-2">150+</div>
          <div class="font-heebo text-[16px] text-neutral-darkest/70">Proyectos completados</div>
        </div>
        
        <div class="text-center">
          <div class="w-16 h-16 bg-primary-green/10 rounded-2xl flex items-center justify-center mx-auto mb-4">
            <Icon name="ph:users-fill" class="w-8 h-8 text-primary-green" />
          </div>
          <div class="font-urbanist font-bold text-[32px] text-primary-green mb-2">500+</div>
          <div class="font-heebo text-[16px] text-neutral-darkest/70">Familias felices</div>
        </div>
      </div>
      
      <!-- Action Buttons -->
      <div 
        class="flex flex-col sm:flex-row gap-4 justify-center items-center pt-4" 
        data-aos="fade-up" 
        data-aos-delay="500"
      >
        <Button 
          href="/proyectos" 
          variant="success"
          size="lg"
          icon="ph:eye-fill"
          iconPosition="left"
        >
          Ver Nuestros Proyectos
        </Button>
        
        <Button 
          href="/contacto" 
          variant="outline"
          size="lg"
          icon="ph:chat-circle-fill"
          iconPosition="left"
        >
          Conversemos
        </Button>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
  
  <!-- Scroll Indicator -->
  <div 
    class="absolute bottom-8 left-1/2 transform -translate-x-1/2 animate-bounce"
    data-aos="fade-in"
    data-aos-delay="800"
  >
    <div class="w-8 h-12 border-2 border-neutral-darkest/30 rounded-full flex justify-center">
      <div class="w-1 h-3 bg-primary-green rounded-full mt-2 animate-pulse"></div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>